title: Ep. 45 Ft Aviane Vargas
itunes:title: Ep. 45 Ft Aviane Vargas
description:
Engine Room Audio studio manager Aviane Vargas stops to have some girl talk with the ladies of Lip Service. They discuss sexual relations with people in the work place, how to tell someone you did not like a gift they brought you, what happens on an all guys trip, using condoms after cheating, is a ring necessary for a proposal and what is an appropriate price for an engagement ring.
